

follow this guide https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/questions/1212156


more specifically

create chrome directory under ~/.mozilla/firefox/

create css file userChrome.css under chrome directory


/*
   Override hiding of Bookmarks Toolbar in F11 full screen
   when you roll down the tabs/main toolbar 
*/
#navigator-toolbox[inFullscreen="true"] #PersonalToolbar {
  visibility: unset !important;
}
